                    <footer class="blockquote-footer mt-2">Analytics Expert <cite title="Source Title">Mike Smith</cite></footer>
                </blockquote>

                <h3 id="key-metrics">Advanced Metrics Revolution</h3>
                <p>The introduction of metrics like Player Efficiency Rating (PER), True Shooting Percentage (TS%), and Win Shares marked the beginning of a new era. These advanced statistics provided deeper insights into player contributions and efficiency.</p>

